The workflow of the unfied approach consists of three stages:

* Conducting fault localization by using existing fault  localization approach
  
  - We employed the [GZoltar](https://github.com/GZoltar) for SBFL
  - We reused the result from learning-based and LLM-based approaches.
* Evaluating the naturalness of a list of candidate statements.
* Combining the suspiciousness score and code naturalness  score, and re-ranking statements
